					<div class='ilt_p' id="thread_content"><p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:-apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont,HelveticaNeue,PingFangSC,HiraginoSansGB,MicrosoftYaHeiUI,MicrosoftYaHei,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:17px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;color:rgb(89,89,89);box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;word-break:normal!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;word-break:normal!important;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;word-break:normal!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;word-break:normal!important;">核心策略：</span></strong></span></strong><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;color:rgb(89,89,89);box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;word-break:normal!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;word-break:normal!important;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;word-break:normal!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;word-break:normal!important;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;color:rgb(255,76,65);word-break:normal!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;word-break:normal!important;">保持底仓，继续耐心等待！</span></strong></span></strong></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:-apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont,HelveticaNeue,PingFangSC,HiraginoSansGB,MicrosoftYaHeiUI,MicrosoftYaHei,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:17px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;"><br style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;"/></p><p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:-apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont,HelveticaNeue,PingFangSC,HiraginoSansGB,MicrosoftYaHeiUI,MicrosoftYaHei,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:17px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-align:justify;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;color:rgb(89,89,89);box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;word-break:normal!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;word-break:normal!important;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;word-break:normal!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;word-break:normal!important;">今日观点：</span></strong></span></strong><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;color:rgb(89,89,89);box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;word-break:normal!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;word-break:normal!important;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;word-break:normal!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;word-break:normal!important;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;color:rgb(255,76,65);word-break:normal!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;word-break:normal!important;">冷血的按照520法则指导自己的操作！</span></strong></span></strong></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:-apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont,HelveticaNeue,PingFangSC,HiraginoSansGB,MicrosoftYaHeiUI,MicrosoftYaHei,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:17px;letter-spacing:0.544px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;"><br style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;"/></p><p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:-apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont,HelveticaNeue,PingFangSC,HiraginoSansGB,MicrosoftYaHeiUI,MicrosoftYaHei,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:17px;letter-spacing:0.544px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;color:rgb(89,89,89);"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;letter-spacing:0.544px;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;">早盘指导</strong></span></span><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;color:rgb(89,89,89);"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;letter-spacing:0.544px;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;">【节前收兵不玩了!】再次明确了对近期盘面变化的观点，大家都知道股市有三种趋势“上涨”、“震荡”“下跌”，按照目前的交易规则，我们能参与的只有“上涨”的阶段，而且为了完成保护本金，大概率获利的基本目标，我们就只能做右侧交易，也就是不妄图买在最低点卖在最高点，只吃“鱼身子”这部分。那么随着昨天中阴线，短线下跌趋势明显，即便要变成上涨也需要一段时间重新整理队形。所以本着炒股不是生活的全部，</strong></span></span><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;color:rgb(89,89,89);word-break:normal!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;word-break:normal!important;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;word-break:normal!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;word-break:normal!important;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;color:rgb(255,76,65);word-break:normal!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;word-break:normal!important;">在不具备交易条件的垃圾时间里，要么自己充电多学理论、多练【斗K】，要么就放松下来走近大自然、走进家庭享受生活！</span></strong></span></strong></span></strong><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;color:rgb(89,89,89);"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;letter-spacing:0.544px;"></span></span></p><p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:-apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont,HelveticaNeue,PingFangSC,HiraginoSansGB,MicrosoftYaHeiUI,MicrosoftYaHei,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:17px;letter-spacing:0.544px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;"><br style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;"/></p><p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:-apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont,HelveticaNeue,PingFangSC,HiraginoSansGB,MicrosoftYaHeiUI,MicrosoftYaHei,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:17px;letter-spacing:0.544px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;color:rgb(89,89,89);"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;letter-spacing:0.544px;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;">距离七十周年国庆的假期仅剩下两个交易日，就是今天和下周一。持币过节的资金大概率在之前已经完成了动作，那么剩下持股过节的卖出的概率也不大，从今天盘面上明显萎缩的成交量也能感受到这一点。走在马路上已经能明显感觉到临近节日的气氛，到处都飘扬着五星红旗，到处都在播放《我和我的祖国》，</strong></span></span><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;color:rgb(89,89,89);word-break:normal!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;word-break:normal!important;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;word-break:normal!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;word-break:normal!important;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;color:rgb(255,76,65);word-break:normal!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;word-break:normal!important;">新中国成立从一穷二白到现在创造众多发展奇迹，人们付出了辛勤劳动，挥洒了汗水，为我们自己感到骄傲和自豪，为我们国家感到骄傲和自豪，祝愿伟大国家民富国强，祝愿伟大的民族繁荣昌盛！</span></strong></span></strong></span></strong><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;color:rgb(89,89,89);"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;letter-spacing:0.544px;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;"><br style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;"/></strong></span></span></p><p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:-apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont,HelveticaNeue,PingFangSC,HiraginoSansGB,MicrosoftYaHeiUI,MicrosoftYaHei,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:17px;letter-spacing:0.544px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;color:rgb(89,89,89);"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;letter-spacing:0.544px;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;"><br style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;"/></strong></span></span></p><p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:-apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont,HelveticaNeue,PingFangSC,HiraginoSansGB,MicrosoftYaHeiUI,MicrosoftYaHei,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:17px;letter-spacing:0.544px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;color:rgb(89,89,89);"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;letter-spacing:0.544px;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;">从今天的行业板块指数来看，硬件和软件两个板块依然表现强势，但是目前从板块指数上看，均跌破了20日均线，按照【王者520法则】20日均线是短期均线中非常重要的指标。同时，指数和个股之间如果出现差异较大的走势时，要区别对待，急速下跌时以指数为主要参考，走势趋缓或者震荡状态时，就可以以个股的走势为主要参考，这里要灵活运用。</strong></span></span><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;color:rgb(89,89,89);font-size:20px;letter-spacing:0.544px;">目前</strong><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;letter-spacing:0.544px;color:rgb(89,89,89);">很多板块指数也都回踩到了重要的55日和89日均线附近，</strong><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;color:rgb(89,89,89);word-break:normal!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;word-break:normal!important;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;word-break:normal!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;word-break:normal!important;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;color:rgb(255,76,65);word-break:normal!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;word-break:normal!important;">沪指和创业板指也是靠近了这两条中期均线，没有明确止跌企稳之前仍需耐心等待！</span></strong></span></strong></span></strong><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;letter-spacing:0.544px;color:rgb(89,89,89);"></strong></p><p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:-apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont,HelveticaNeue,PingFangSC,HiraginoSansGB,MicrosoftYaHeiUI,MicrosoftYaHei,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:17px;letter-spacing:0.544px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;letter-spacing:0.544px;color:rgb(89,89,89);"><br style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;"/></strong></p><p style="margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;clear:both;min-height:1em;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:-apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont,HelveticaNeue,PingFangSC,HiraginoSansGB,MicrosoftYaHeiUI,MicrosoftYaHei,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:17px;letter-spacing:0.544px;white-space:normal;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;letter-spacing:0.544px;color:rgb(89,89,89);">从上午沪指和创业板指的走势来看，双双明显缩量，其中创业板指反弹幅度较大，且站上了610日均线；而沪指则是小星形线的状态，最低点回踩到了89日均线。直播中已经明确了“由于创业板610天线并没有有效击破，这里不建议空仓过节，前高听王者建议减仓的股民朋友，目前持有底仓过节即可，不过底仓必须符合王者语音课与碎片语音课选股要领！”</strong><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;color:rgb(89,89,89);word-break:normal!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;word-break:normal!important;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;word-break:normal!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;word-break:normal!important;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;color:rgb(255,76,65);word-break:normal!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;word-break:normal!important;">我们要对市场保持敬畏和谨慎的态度，但是不要恐惧和恐慌，对于祖国未来的发展我们充满希望和信心，坚定自己的操作策略，做睡得着觉的交易，过快乐健康的生活！</span></strong></span></strong></span></strong><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;letter-spacing:0.544px;color:rgb(89,89,89);"></strong></p><p><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;color:rgb(89,89,89);word-break:normal!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;word-break:normal!important;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;word-break:normal!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;font-size:20px;word-break:normal!important;"><strong style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;color:rgb(255,76,65);word-break:normal!important;"><span style="margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;box-sizing:border-box!important;word-wrap:break-word!important;word-break:normal!important;"><br/></span></strong></span></strong></span></strong></p><p><br/></p></div>
